<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="about-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>About Nageshwaram Foundation Trust</h1>
                <p>Dedicated to fostering educational growth and community development in rural India.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="trust-story-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Journey of Empowerment</h2>
                <p>The Nageshwaram Foundation Trust was established with a profound vision: to bring accessible and quality education to the heart of rural India. Founded by visionary educators and philanthropists, our journey began with the understanding that education is the most powerful tool for societal transformation. Since our inception, we have been committed to breaking down barriers to learning and creating pathways to brighter futures for countless children and young adults.</p>
                <p>Our work extends beyond traditional schooling. We believe in holistic development, which includes academic excellence, character building, skill development, and community engagement. We strive to create an environment where every student feels empowered to explore their potential and contribute meaningfully to society.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="our-philosophy-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Guiding Philosophy</h2>
                <p>At Nageshwaram Foundation Trust, our philosophy is rooted in compassion, integrity, and a relentless pursuit of excellence. We believe in:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Accessibility:** Ensuring that quality education reaches every child, regardless of their socio-economic background or geographical location.</li>
                    <li>**Quality Education:** Providing modern learning facilities, qualified educators, and an updated curriculum that prepares students for the challenges of tomorrow.</li>
                    <li>**Holistic Development:** Nurturing intellectual, emotional, social, and physical growth, fostering well-rounded individuals.</li>
                    <li>**Community Engagement:** Working hand-in-hand with parents, local leaders, and community members to create a supportive ecosystem for learning.</li>
                    <li>**Sustainability:** Building educational initiatives that are long-lasting and continue to serve future generations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Join Us in Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Your support can help us reach more children and expand our educational endeavors. Learn how you can be a part of this noble cause.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary">Contact Us to Support</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
